data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
Some games can be restored to a alternative library.
To use this feature select a game from the list on the left. If this game has this feature available, a new library location will be selectable from the drop down box.
If you want to add a new library location to this list, you can now safely start Steam and navigate to: View -> Settings -> Downloads + Cloud -> Steam Library Folders When finished close steam and click 'Refresh List' below.
